集、保藏、利用、对外提供我国人类遗传资源应当尊重人类遗传资源提供者的隐私权，事先取得知情同意，确保提供者健康并保护其合法权益。在我国境内采集、保藏和对外提供我国人类遗传资源必须由我国科研机构、高等学校、医疗机构和企业开展。境外组织、个人及其设立或者实际控制的机构不得在我国境内采集、保藏我国人类遗传资源，不得向境外提供我国人类遗传资源。科技部拟规定：不得向境外提供我国人类遗传资源"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-6592cac50e3028c18000a1ed9ea1f18e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/523485310"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Irq+uqKOw8OsVEAMaCDc4NjExNTA4IPHt5pEGMAg45ANALHIJNTIzNDg1MzEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1648159759.06314", "card_id": "Q_522206035", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 118}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日本发动机十分先进，却敢向任何一国出售，为何不怕技术泄露？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-9d8e99ca093b91a13f6a8a277aba9592_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/522206035"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Irq+uqKOw8OsVEAMaCDc4MzI3NjcxIODoxJEGMAw40gJALXIJNTIyMjA2MDM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1648159759.0635667", "card_id": "Q_523799654", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 219}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《海贼王》1044 话完整版已出，你的感受如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "之前是 1044 话的情报，目前 1044 话的日文版已经全都有了"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-55fa769cccb02f49262d9767450a0d4a_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/523799654"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Irq+uqKOw8OsVEAMaCDc4NjgxNTMwIJTR75EGMBQ4lwNALnIJNTIzNzk5NjU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1648159759.0640345", "